list.item:

   Skin and Subcutaneous Tissue Disorders: 
Severe skin reactions, including toxic epidermal necrolysis and Stevens-Johnson syndrome [see Warnings and Precautions (5.6)
]; drug reaction with eosinophilia and systemic symptoms (DRESS) [see Warnings and Precautions (5.7)]; psoriasis or worsening of psoriasis (including pustular psoriasis and nail psoriasis); nail disorders
